casebody.data:
Roderick NUNLEY, petitioner,
v.
Michael S. BOWERSOX. No. 15-5605 (15A163). Supreme Court of the United States Sept. 1, 2015.

*24Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice ALITO and by him referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit denied.
